{"about_the_game":"The Witcher Adventure Game is a digital adaptation of CD PROJEKT RED\u2019s board game set in the brutal fantasy universe of monster slayer Geralt of Rivia. Travel across the beautifully rendered world of The Witcher and complete a variety of quests \u2014 hunt deadly beasts, solve ancient mysteries, and more.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303800/extras/TWAG1.gif?t=1721645960\" /><br><br>Take on the role of one of four distinct characters known from the books and video games: monster slayer Geralt of Rivia\u037e cunning sorceress Triss Merigold\u037e dwarven warrior Yarpen Zigrin\u037e and roguish bard Dandelion. Each character has unique skills and multiple ways of overcoming obstacles \u2014 the choice is yours: do you fight your way to victory, call on your charm or try your hand at diplomacy?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303800/extras/TWAG2.gif?t=1721645960\" /><br><br>Explore a land of mystery and spin your own unique tale each time you play. The Witcher Adventure Game is set in the rich universe created by internationally renowned novelist Andrzej Sapkowski. Whether you\u2019re a long time fan or this is your first contact with The Witcher universe, The Witcher Adventure Game will pull you in with its deep backstory and high replayability.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303800/extras/TWAG3.gif?t=1721645960\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple, easy to understand rules, and intuitive gameplay mechanics<br></li><li>4 unique heroes with different skills and approaches to problem solving<br></li><li>Over 288 cards to discover and 30 monsters to deal with<br></li><li>Art design taken straight from the critically acclaimed Witcher series of video games<br></li><li>Different gameplay modes: play against AI or your friends, with options for both online multiplayer and hot seat<br></li><li>Achievement and leaderboard support</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Don't walk away","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/303800/9edb436188afe1fc04a60b37418ab1851a408e2b.jpg"},{"name":"Overachiever","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/303800/51c2d41b73e268cd82c02e3e83a009a5b94cc320.jpg"},{"name":"The next best thing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/303800/7283059ffef672bca85745bb1995ae1dcec01b95.jpg"},{"name":"Helping Hand","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/303800/284e1cffd450c57af1b2b5ddcf0108c93c5b6074.jpg"},{"name":"Die die my darling","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/303800/aa04d9693c007b5b36a92066be4a14d2e72bec78.jpg"},{"name":"Where am I going to put all this?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/303800/db78db444eb6e12f7f6cf6db0eab14d1acb4ea4a.jpg"},{"name":"Welcome to Vivaldi Bank!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/303800/53a7b56b325f0e501e317e3ee430aa31ccedf36b.jpg"},{"name":"Vivaldi's best client","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/303800/6a7c8f286fbc366650b70d008223746298907215.jpg"},{"name":"Shut up and take my money!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/303800/af6cfdf1af059df63fd425f58ea5b118fd24e810.jpg"},{"name":"Shani would be impressed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/303800/d51b4a0b44da0ef1702ec3ceed16a2777d054a67.jpg"}],"total":37},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303800/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1721645960","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_a